'''Janet Carafa''' is a mime artist based in [[New York City]]
who also runs New York Entertainment Connection, an event entertainment and production company.  She has studied with [[Marcel Marceau]] and was a lead performer with the American Mime Theatre for eight years. She has also directed the Movement and Mime Theatre.

Originally from Connecticut and a graduate of the [[University of Colorado at Boulder|University of Colorado]], Ms. Carafa has performed with the New York City Mime Company and the Valley Studio for Mime in [[Wisconsin]]. 

